pithist(m, type = "random", nsim = 10, fill = "darkgray", alpha = 1, col = "black",
  ref = FALSE, confint = FALSE, simint = FALSE)
@

Probabilistic calibration:
\begin{itemize}
\item[-] PIT residuals: $u_i = F(y_i | \, \hat{\boldsymbol{\theta}}_i)$.
\item[-] Compare: Uniform.
\end{itemize}

\end{column}

